# P4CE Design System

Source of truth: `_design/tokens/tokens.json`

## Product principles
- Fast over flashy
- Minimal UI, dark mode first
- One-handed interaction
- Zero spreadsheet feeling, minimal typing
- Instant interactions — no skeleton screens, no loading walls

## Color palette (dark mode only)

| Token      | Hex       | Usage |
|------------|-----------|-------|
| `bg`       | `#121418` | Main app background |
| `bgDeep`   | `#0C0F13` | Tab bar, deepest background |
| `surf`     | `#1C2026` | Cards, stat tiles, hero cards |
| `surfHi`   | `#252B33` | Elevated elements, date badges |
| `line`     | `#363D47` | Borders, dividers, inactive bars |
| `lineSoft` | `#272E38` | Subtle separators |
| `text`     | `#F7F7F0` | Primary text, headings, values |
| `textDim`  | `#C4C4B8` | Secondary text, supporting info |
| `muted`    | `#6B7280` | Metadata caps, timestamps |
| `dim`      | `#3F4550` | Inactive tab icons, de-emphasized |
| `lime`     | `#D4F53C` | **PRIMARY ACCENT** — CTA, PRs, highlights |
| `limeDeep` | `#9EBF1A` | Pressed / active state of lime |
| `limeInk`  | `#1A2605` | Text / icons ON lime background |
| `red`      | `#E05A3A` | Danger, pain flags, low readiness |
| `amber`    | `#F0C040` | Warning, medium readiness (5–6/10) |
| `green`    | `#5DBF78` | Success, high readiness label |

## Typography

| Role          | Font           | Size      | Weight | Notes |
|---------------|----------------|-----------|--------|-------|
| `heroWorkout` | Antonio        | 68–76 pt  | 700    | Tracking −1.4 to −1.6 |
| `heroSub`     | Antonio        | 18–22 pt  | 500    | Tracking +0.4 |
| `statsLarge`  | Antonio        | 24–30 pt  | 600–700| Tracking −0.5 |
| `ctaLabel`    | Antonio        | 26–30 pt  | 700    | Tracking +1.5 |
| `sectionDate` | Geist          | 14–22 pt  | 500–600| Tracking −0.3 |
| `sessionName` | Geist          | 13–16 pt  | 500    | |
| `metadataCaps`| JetBrains Mono | 9–11 pt   | 500–600| UPPERCASE, tracking +1.3–1.6 |
| `tagLabel`    | JetBrains Mono | 10 pt     | 500    | UPPERCASE, tracking +1.6 |

- Display font (Antonio) → hero numbers, workout names, CTAs, big stats
- Body font (Geist) → labels, session names, body text
- Mono font (JetBrains Mono) → metadata CAPS, dates, tags

## Spacing scale (pt)
4 · 8 · 12 · 16 · 20 · 24 · 32 · 40 · 48 · 64

## Corner radius
`sm` 8 · `md` 12 · `lg` 16 · `xl` 20 · `2xl` 22 (hero cards) · `3xl` 24 (full-bleed CTA) · `full` 999

## Canvas
- Screen: 402 × 874 pt (iPhone 17 Pro logical)
- Safe area: top 59 pt, bottom 34 pt
- Content width: 362 pt (16 pt side padding each side)
- Tab bar height: 83 pt

## Design inspiration
Strong · Hevy · TrainHeroic · Athlytic
Desired feeling: **"minimal training notebook for serious athletes"**
